skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: aussie rules
des:
Aussie Rules is your AFL mate. Ask for round tips, or just a game tip. Ask for tips for a future round. Although Alexa is smart, she consults with 16 different computer models to decide how to tip a game. You may also ask for a last game result, how my tipping is going, or even for a random footy stat.

Things you can say include, "Ask Aussie Rules who will win next round", "Ask Aussie Rules what are your tips for round 18", "Ask Aussie Rules what were your tips for round 1", "Ask Aussie Rules who won the Saints game?", "Ask Aussie Rules who will win the Cats game?", "Ask Aussie Rules how's your tipping going?", or "Ask Aussie Rules for a random stat".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
